title: Bugs Bunny Halloween Collection (2 DVD)
description:
A fine collection of 16 classic Looney Tunes cartoons with a spooky Halloween theme, just on time for October 31!

DVD 1 is an adaptation of the old Bugs Bunny Road Runner Show including original intro, credits and a sprinkling of vintage Bugs Bunny cereal commercials from the 60&#039;s.  Also included are these classic shorts:

Broom-Stick Bunny
Claws For Alarm
Hair-Raising Hare
The Last Hungry Cat
Bewitched Bunny
Hyde And Hare
Scaredy Cat
Water, Water Every Hare
A-Haunting We Will Go
Transylvania 6-5000

DVD 2 is a bonus and includes excerpts from an old Laser-Disc called Looney Tunes After Dark, with thanks to dahulk12 for the original torrent of avi&#039;s.  I&#039;ve excluded a few shorts from this title because they appear on DVD 1 in better quality.  That being said, DVD 2 is still very watchable.  Included are:

Jumpin&#039; Jupiter
The Night Of The Living Duck
Hyde And Tweet
Hare-Way To The Stars
The Duxorcist
The Hasty Hare

These DVD&#039;s are made for fun and enjoyment!  Please seed and have a Happy Halloween!
